{"surahDetails":{"id":102,"arabicName":"التكاثر","banglaName":"প্রাচুর্যের প্রতিযোগিতা","englishName":"Competition","enTranslatedName":"At-Takathur","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/102.mp3","totalAyah":8},"surah":{"id":102,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","bangl_text":"প্রাচুর্যের লালসা তোমাদেরকে গাফেল রাখে","english_text":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6169.mp3","colorText":"أَلْهَ[n[ـٰ]كُمُ [h:14627[ٱ][l[ل]تَّكَاثُرُ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"أَلْهَ<span class=madda_normal>ـٰ</span>كُمُ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span><span class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</span>تَّكَاثُرُ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","bangl_text":"এমনকি, তোমরা কবরস্থানে পৌছে যাও।","english_text":"Until you visit the graveyards","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6170.mp3","colorText":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ [h:14628[ٱ]لْمَقَابِرَ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"حَتَّىٰ زُرْتُمُ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْمَقَابِرَ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"No! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6171.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم[p[ُو]نَ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم<span class=madda_permissible>ُو</span>نَ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"Then no! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6172.mp3","colorText":"ثُ[g[مّ]َ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم[p[ُو]نَ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ثُ<span class=ghunnah>مّ</span>َ كَلَّا سَوْفَ تَعْلَم<span class=madda_permissible>ُو</span>نَ <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","bangl_text":"কখনই নয়; যদি তোমরা নিশ্চিত জানতে।","english_text":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6173.mp3","colorText":"كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ [h:14629[ٱ]لْيَق[p[ِي]نِ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"كَلَّا لَوْ تَعْلَمُونَ عِلْمَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْيَق<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>نِ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","bangl_text":"তোমরা অবশ্যই জাহান্নাম দেখবে","english_text":"You will surely see the Hellfire","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6174.mp3","colorText":"لَتَرَوُ[g[نّ]َ [h:14630[ٱ]لْجَح[p[ِي]مَ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"لَتَرَوُ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْجَح<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>مَ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তোমরা তা অবশ্যই দেখবে দিব্য প্রত্যয়ে","english_text":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/6175.mp3","colorText":"ثُ[g[مّ]َ لَتَرَوُ[g[نّ]َهَا عَيْنَ [h:14631[ٱ]لْيَق[p[ِي]نِ","juz":30,"ruku":544,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ثُ<span class=ghunnah>مّ</span>َ لَتَرَوُ<span class=ghunnah>نّ</span>َهَا عَيْنَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْيَق<span class=madda_permissible>ِي</span>نِ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","bangl_text":"এরপর অবশ্যই সেদিন তোমরা নেয়ামত সম